        {
            "title": "導演會頒獎禮丨Lokman拒提咖啡店結業蝕幾多 做生意當上一課：唔跌唔大！ Dee指保錡無消失過好快會現身",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"導演會頒獎禮丨Lokman拒提咖啡店生意蝕幾多 結業當上一課：唔跌唔大！ Dee指保錡無消失過好快會現身\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/3fd38b9bf34eff119de8dce04b127bd4/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250310/_2025031023200095341.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">導演會頒獎禮丨Lokman拒提咖啡店生意蝕幾多 結業當上一課：唔跌唔大！ Dee指保錡無消失過好快會現身</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>男團MIRROR成員楊樂文（Lokman）、江𤒹生（AK）、邱傲然（Tiger）、王智德（Alton）、陳瑞輝（Frankie）、以及ERROR的何啟華（Dee）到尖東出席「香港電影導演會周年晚宴暨年度頒獎典禮」。6子齊齊受訪，問到是否出席活動接觸導演「搲撈」？Lokman笑言會和導演傾偈，和導演說自己最近好得閒，問到想拍甚麼電影？Frankie笑言想拍紀錄片。問可會減價接戲？Lokman指有好劇本沒問題，AK形容未有資格「向錢看」，只能盡力和導演表示自己得閒拍戲。\n\n</p><h2>不認識「阿嫂」林明禎</h2>\n<p>Lokman指最近忙拍新電影，好有神秘感，問到忙工作導致顧不及生意而令咖啡店結業？他指不是，拍戲是最近的事，又形容「做生意當上了一課，是非常昂貴又寶貴的經驗，看將來會不會再做生意學習。」談到MIRROR成員做生意先後結業，可會覺得不適合？Lokman稱不覺得，又指很多人都不是做生意便成功，都需要學習。問到蝕本多少？他說：「不講了，傷心事，講起都痛！小朋友不跌不會大，下次小心些！」談到林明禎在場可會照顧「阿嫂」，他們即笑言誰是「阿嫂」，又指私人事交給他們本人，私下和明禎不認識。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Lokman、AK、Tiger、Alton、Frankie、以及Dee出席「香港電影導演會周年晚宴暨年度頒獎典禮」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2a7a5f8788b2bb852e81b2108062f0ce/2025-03/_DSC4101.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Lokman、AK、Tiger、Alton、Frankie、以及Dee出席「香港電影導演會周年晚宴暨年度頒獎典禮」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"問到Lokman咖啡店生意蝕本多少？他表示不講了，傷心事！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/19079253e952014a6c1eb14e022c4cc0/2025-03/_DSC4111.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        問到Lokman咖啡店生意蝕本多少？他表示不講了，傷心事！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"AK眼鏡Look現身。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/de311f73ed38cf0f83b78b0dc4d36602/2025-03/_DSC4117.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        AK眼鏡Look現身。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Dee透露保錡很好，問到何時會現身，他說好快啦！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bf55abe27e8efe01f65d59da64405343/2025-03/_DSC4122.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Dee透露保錡很好，問到何時會現身，他說好快啦！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Lokman透露最近忙拍新電影。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0df5d36c7383ad1666a789932024f7e0/2025-03/_DSC4308.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Lokman透露最近忙拍新電影。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Frankie \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b68eb5f1e293c1558ce9a73b24ad16a0/2025-03/_DSC4106.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Frankie \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Alton\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2e5dc634380aefdfdb34fea8501e4d2d/2025-03/_DSC4108.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Alton\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"保錡因「ViuTV叻仔」事件引脫粉潮。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a261940682e2da13d909a0e4c7ebc4e9/2025-03/22_9.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        保錡因「ViuTV叻仔」事件引脫粉潮。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>ERROR成員沒因「ViuTV叻仔」受牽連</h2>\n<p>而何啟華被問及隊友吳保錡「ViuTV叻仔」事件後消失及脫粉一事，問到可有關心隊友，他指保錡很好，問到何時會現身，他稱：「好快啦，他沒有消失過！（有指ERROR成員受牽連？）我無事，你看我今次身光頸靚出來便知沒事。」又透露自己正經營一些新工作，相信很快可以公開。\n\n</p>\n<p><br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2057415/即時-娛樂-導演會頒獎禮丨Lokman拒提咖啡店結業蝕幾多-做生意當上一課-唔跌唔大-Dee指保錡無消失過好快會現身",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-10 23:26:21",
